entry.title: derivator/tafkars
entry.summary:
Tafkars

Tafkars stands for "The API formerly known as...", is written in Rust and is pronounced like "tough cars".

  • tafkars contains API bindings for that one site that people used to love.
  • tafkars-lemmy is an API proxy that allows apps to talk to Lemmy through a familiar API from a kinder time.

Help wanted

There is still lots of work to be done, especially on tafkars-lemmy. Pull requests welcome!
